{"tid":125762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲向太撐警施暴： 打到你們清醒為止","createTime":"2017-02-18T18:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T13:37:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c05d7ffa4eb7bb6d1996c21a27719043625c7007","tid":125762,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:05:46.000Z","msg":"尋晚（11月30日）學聯同學民思潮喺集會期間宣佈行動升級，號召在場佔領人士包圍政府總部同特首辦，有人因為佔領人士被警方暴力對待而心痛，但藍絲向太（陳嵐）就喺微博開post，表示要「一個個打到你們頭腦清醒為止」，力撐警察暴力清場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20141201/large/1417417909_9231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20141201%2Flarge%2F1417417909_9231.jpg&h=f24687ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（12月1日）下午，向太轉發親中報章對於尋晚金鐘集會嘅報導，話睇新聞嬲到想砸爛電視機：「可惡的佔中破壞香港美麗形象的混蛋。還好不是我做警務局長，不然的話你們統統跑不了，一個個打到你們頭腦清醒為止。全部都抓去坐牢而且不準保釋！」<br />\n<br />\n一向反佔中嘅向太更直言香港政府太仁慈、太忍讓佔領人士，仲叫佢哋返屋企。微博係強國人嘅天下，向太嘅言論當然獲得強國網友力撐，仲有人支持佢做警務處處長，解決破壞份子、還香港和平咁話。向太做「一姐」，咪即係同禿鷹爭嘢做？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20141201/large/1417417967_2a5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20141201%2Flarge%2F1417417967_2a5f.jpg&h=ad99f9f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20141201/117280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20141201%2F117280&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bc8ad7ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20141201%2F117280&h=05a25892\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20141201/117280</a>"},{"pid":"6066b2db92a8602419833536743a1e574f8a1181","tid":125762,"uid":340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:13:46.000Z","msg":"返屋企幫老公含撚啦"},{"pid":"5f336f2f62891d026006529282b525c889c0b9d3","tid":125762,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislik